sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Visitor
    participant ContactUI as Home Contact Component
    participant Validation as Zod Validation Layer
    participant MsgAPI as POST /api/messages
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant MailService as Mail Service (Nodemailer + Gmail SMTP)
    participant Dashboard as Dashboard Messages Page

    Visitor->>ContactUI: Fill name, email, subject, message
    ContactUI->>Validation: Validate payload

    alt Invalid payload
        Validation-->>ContactUI: Validation errors
        ContactUI-->>Visitor: Render field errors
    else Valid payload
        Validation-->>ContactUI: Sanitized payload
        ContactUI->>MsgAPI: Submit inquiry
        MsgAPI->>DB: Create MESSAGE row (isRead=false)
        DB-->>MsgAPI: Message ID + timestamp
        MsgAPI->>MailService: Dispatch admin + visitor emails
        MailService-->>MsgAPI: Delivery accepted
        MsgAPI-->>ContactUI: 201 Created
        ContactUI-->>Visitor: Success confirmation

        Dashboard->>MsgAPI: GET /api/messages?status=new
        MsgAPI->>DB: Query unread messages
        DB-->>MsgAPI: Unread message list
        MsgAPI-->>Dashboard: Message previews

        Note over MsgAPI,MailService: Detailed SMTP flow is documented in contact_submission_email_delivery_sequence.mmd
    end
